'''''Imfura''''', ni filime ngufi yo mu [[Rwanda|Rwanda yo muri]] 2017 iyobowe na Samuel Ishimwe ikaba yarayikoranye na Daniel Schweizer na Jean Perret kuri Haute École d'Art et de Design (HEAD) na Imitana Productions.   Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Moses Mwizerwa mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Kijyana Yves na Nyirababikira Hadidja mu nshingano zabo.

Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.  Bibaye umusaruro wambere wu [[Rwanda]] washyizwe mumarushanwa ya Berlinale Short. Muri make yatsindiye icyiciro cya silver Bear Jury Igiciro cya Berlin International Festival Festival . 

== Umugambi ==
Iyi filime ivuga ku nkuru yashyizwe mu [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Rwanda nyuma ya jenoside]] . 

